headline: AT&T (T) Post Q3 Earnings: Buy, Sell, or Hold?
summary: AT&T has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 20.2%. The stock now trades at $23.07, marking a 33.6% gain. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
